eaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E overcorrects\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDefinitely needs some polishing\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhat I try to do in those situations is disabling \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E and manually rotating the vessel to the disired position, after which (if the vessel is completely stable) re-enabling \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E (and if necessary clicking a certain action button)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-26T16:45:24Z\u0022 title=\u002204/26/2023 04:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 26, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by LowSnow\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EPossible solution added\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}